{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4ff5dfbea4","title":"在中共赣南省委召集的省、县、区三级主要干部会议上的讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6f08f75429","index":0,"year":1934,"month":10,"day":15,"articleId":"4ff5dfbea4"}],"tags":[{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji7-2","name":"毛泽东全集第7卷(2)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji7-2.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji7-2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"71c2f8ccb5","type":"paragraph","text":"在中共赣南省委召集的省、县、区","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"4ff5dfbea4"},{"id":"ec163a9824","type":"paragraph","text":"三级主要干部会议上的讲话”","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"4ff5dfbea4"},{"id":"ce8ed70721","type":"paragraph","text":"（1934年10月15日）","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"4ff5dfbea4"},{"id":"a5c07e92d5","type":"paragraph","text":"敌人这次进攻苏区，采用的是堡垒政策，一直打到我们中央苏区门口，企图断水捉鱼，全部地消灭红军。我们红军主力部队要冲破敌人的封锁线，到敌人后方去，打击敌人，消灭敌人","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"4ff5dfbea4"},{"id":"79874da2bb","type":"paragraph","text":"你们这些在地方工作的干部，仍然留在苏区，团结人民，开展游击战争。你们不要怕，不要认为红军主力部队走了，革命就失败了。不能只看到暂时的困难，要看到革命是有希望的，红军一定会回来的！","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"4ff5dfbea4"},{"id":"1ea2075d8a","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]1934年10月15日，中共赣南省委召集的省、县、区三级主要干部","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"4ff5dfbea4"}],"page":{"id":"2c9496a9cd","publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"4ff5dfbea4","start":53,"end":53}}}},"__N_SSG":true}